    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but what do you mean by \"letting go\"? because even when i'm alone it doesn't feel like i'm actually being myself. it just feels like there's nothing there. like i'm just a ghost drifting through everyone else's lives. it's not even about being relaxed, it's just... the effort of existing feels so heavy lately. i don't see the point in it anymore.",
