    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you, but it's not just about being an \"outlier.\" it's the weight of it all. it feels like i'm carrying something heavy that i can't ever put down. you talk about letting go being liberating... but for me, it feels more like there's no way to actually find peace while i'm still here. like, is there even a version of this where the exhaustion just stops?",
